<h1>You're invited to <%= @competition_name %>!</h1>
<p>Dear <%= @invite_code.first_name %>,</p>
<p>This email contains information for signing up to our online dashboard.
  From here, you'll be able to learn from our coding courses, keep up to date
  on the latest news and updates from the venue, as well as keeping track of
  workshops and events that happen during the weekend.</p>

<p>To create your account, either follow the link below:</p>

<p><a href="<%= new_user_registration_url(code: @invite_code.code) %>">Login link</a></p>

<p>Or you can visit the sign up page and enter your access code:</p>

<p>URL: <%= new_user_registration_url %></p>

<p>Code: <%= @invite_code.code %></p>

<p>We look forward to seeing you at the event!</p>

<p>Kind regards,</p>

<p>The <%= @competition_name %> team</p>
